Package javelin.model.world

Enum Season

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Season>
      • javelin.model.world.Season
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Season>
    public enum Season
extends java.lang.Enum<Season>
    Four seasons. The starting season for a world is random and each seasons lasts for days. Different seasons (and times of day) have different effects on Terrain hazards and events.
    Author:
    alex
    See Also:
    Javelin.getDayPeriod()
